  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Prospective, observational, cohort study to evaluate the reliability of preoperative work-up
      of patients submitted to surgery for pancreatic cystic neoplasms, in a tertiary referral
      center. A comparison between the preoperative diagnostic suspicion and the final pathologic
      report will be done.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
